6566 per patient grady hospital would have to buy the drug at a 
yearly cost of 8000 to 10000 per patient and would ultimately 
pay an estimated 1 million per year to continue the azt program 
he said 
dhr officials said there were 1493 aids cases reported in 
georgia as of june 1988 with 841 deaths 
