the first half down from 239 million or 159 per share in the 
same period a year earlier the 1987 figure includes a 140 million 
charge for the relocation of penneys headquarters to dallas from 
new york 
firsthalf revenue totaled 639 billion down from 663 
billion in the first six months of 1987 
